Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道谢的人应该是我
