Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有飞碟在会很难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再来拜托一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到烟花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到许可的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花  烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花  烟花  烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的烟花啊  就是飞到高空中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是烟花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  7年前在祭会时照的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花会从湖面升起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪叽啪叽啪叽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的话  我可以把相簿借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别借给你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}诺艾尔  危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧过来吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:08:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还留着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用一周时间准备烟花大会  怎么可能办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要飞碟还在这里  就不可能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是你擅自决定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有烟花又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要放了烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我就会高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始只是想让柚季你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时候的大家  一起看烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽在自说自话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  差不多该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川同学也要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果烟花  能放出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要和你说
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为柚季再也不会和我说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才和乃乃香在一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从那时候开始就一直在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香对7年前的事情一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都不知道  却打算放烟花？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是傻瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香没有看不起你所做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正想说的  是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:12:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道乃乃香能不能做出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想问你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和乃乃香是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你们是何时何地认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个下雪的日子  她教会了我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要唱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要糊弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且自从乃乃香回到这个小镇后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有下过雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音真清楚乃乃香的事情呢  好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为乃乃香是个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃完好吃的东西后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会露出笑容的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在晚上偷偷跑出家门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己弄伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}错的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明让你帮了这么多忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香相信的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后能够实现就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  关于那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是有其他事情想拜托您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我必须要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友们约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花一放完  就去桥那边集合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去吗  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过作为交换…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要注意安全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春  今天店里很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以擅自跑去看祭典哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先声明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季的事我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看她自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便没有烟花？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  这和诺艾尔没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔看见大家喜笑颜开  会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季不是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香都笑开花了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这海报…是那个时候的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得真晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花还是没能放成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  必须要道歉的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向乃乃香  向小春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  全都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果  只能放我带来的线香花火了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带来的放了七年都吸足了水分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是户川同学也在就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}线香花火真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常地  非常地…
